    "text": "Debt Ceiling Reform Act\n\nThis bill replaces the existing federal debt limit with procedures that allow the Department of the Treasury to continue issuing additional debt unless a joint resolution of disapproval regarding the additional debt is enacted into law.\u00a0The bill also requires Congress to consider the joint resolution using specified expedited legislative procedures.\u00a0"
